\par \pard\plain \s24\ql\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ltrpar\cf2\dbch\af9\langfe2052\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1081\kerning1\loch\f3\fs24\lang1033{\listtext\pard\plain \scaps0\caps0\cf1\strike0\i0\ulnone\ulc0\b0\dbch\af10\fs22 \u9679\'3f\tab}\ilvl0\ls2 \li1440\ri0\lin1440\rin0\fi360\li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi360{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
If you are able to avoid SIM registration - either because it is not mandated in your country or because you are able to obtain a SIM without registering - it is harder for your identity to be linked to your phone and SIM card. Please note that we are NOT suggesting that you break any country laws.}
\par \pard\plain \s24\ql\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ltrpar\cf2\dbch\af9\langfe2052\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1081\kerning1\loch\f3\fs24\lang1033{\listtext\pard\plain \scaps0\caps0\cf1\strike0\i0\ulnone\ulc0\b0\dbch\af10\fs22 \u9679\'3f\tab}\ilvl0\ls2 \li1440\ri0\lin1440\rin0\fi360\li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi360{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
If SIM registration is not mandatory in another country and you are able to obtain a prepaid SIM card in that country without registering, you may be able to roam in your home country with that SIM card. Callls will be expensive to make and receive, so be prepared to only use this SIM when you really need to be anonymous. Note that you may also attract unwanted attention by doing this.}
\par \pard\plain \s24\ql\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ltrpar\cf2\dbch\af9\langfe2052\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1081\kerning1\loch\f3\fs24\lang1033{\listtext\pard\plain \scaps0\caps0\cf1\strike0\i0\ulnone\ulc0\b0\dbch\af10\fs22 \u9679\'3f\tab}\ilvl0\ls2 \li1440\ri0\lin1440\rin0\fi360\li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi360{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
Use prepaid SIM cards only, change them regularly, and buy credit using cash only. Remember that an adversary may still use your \u8216\'91human network\u8217\'92 - who you call, places where you are seen making a call - to identify you.}
